+of+Night+and+Flame">Sword of Night and Flame</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;♦&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class= "wiki_link" href="//eldenring.wiki.fextralife.com/Sword+of+St+Trina">Sword of St Trina</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;♦&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class= "wiki_link" href="//eldenring.wiki.fextralife.com/Warhawk's+Talon">Warhawk's Talon</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;♦&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class= "wiki_link" href="//eldenring.wiki.fextralife.com/Weathered+Straight+Sword">Weathered Straight Sword</a></div></td> 
